      2           *  @file  AlternateLoad.c
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Basic description of file contents
      5           *
      6           *  @details     This module Defines & controls the Valve position
      7           *               This module process the valve position as the request came from application & set the valve position 1,2 or 3.
      8           *               After reset it completes the one rotation and hit to the initial position.
